    <item>
      <title>波音的危机之年让投资者对股价下跌保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/boeing-s-year-of-crisis-leaves-investors-wary-of-beaten-up-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司原本有望实现复苏的一年，却遭遇了 2008 年以来最严重的股市暴跌。如果华尔街的预测正确，那么这家飞机制造商的股价在 2025 年可能只会温和回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/boeing-s-year-of-crisis-leaves-investors-wary-of-beaten-up-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳当选总统称国际货币基金组织协议将限制激进改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/ghana-s-president-elect-says-imf-deal-to-cap-radical-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳新任总统约翰·马哈马表示，国际货币基金组织的融资计划将限制其政府立即采取彻底改革的能力。一周前，选民们给予他沉重的使命，要求他解决该国沉重的债务负担和高昂的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/ghana-s-president-elect-says-imf-deal-to-cap-radical-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 11:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世贸组织总干事称开放的全球贸易是养活世界人口的唯一途径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/open-global-trade-is-only-way-to-feed-the-world-wto-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界贸易组织总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔·伊韦阿拉表示，如果世界不努力维持稳定和开放的贸易体系，全球贫困将会增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/open-global-trade-is-only-way-to-feed-the-world-wto-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 09:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BC Partners 即将将 Synthon 出售给高盛资产管理公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bc-partners-is-said-to-near-sale-of-synthon-to-goldman-asset-arm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，BC Partners 即将达成协议，将荷兰仿制药制造商 Synthon International Holding BV 出售给高盛资产管理公司。]]></description>
